highlights.text: “おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 144 days straight.
CHAEYOUNG has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “AVOCADO (feat. Gliiico)” is the highest at #18.
“Wake Me up When September Ends” by Green Day is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 57 spots at #7.
“GIRL” by CHAEYOUNG is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #79.
